# Migration targets — explicitly track ecosystem content under docs/
# even though filenames may match the ignore patterns above. The negations
# below let docs/{specs,superpowers,archived-specs,roadmap}/** through
# while keeping root-level *_SPEC.md, *PLAN.md, etc. as local-only working
# drafts.
!docs/specs/**
!docs/superpowers/**
!docs/archived-specs/**
!docs/roadmap/**
!docs/metrics-contract.md
!docs/testing.md
!docs/COSTOPTIMISATION.md
!docs/DEMO-IMPROVEMENT-SPEC.md

# Local backups created by the auto-memory retirement plan (2026-06-04)
*.bak
